#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_guide.md:3
msgid "Trainer Meetings"
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_guide.md:4
msgid ""
"The Trainers group meets regularly. Our meetings include three sections: 1) "
"Discussion, where we share experiences and get advice about running "
"instructor training events, 2) Announcements, and 3) Topic of the Month, "
"which may include curriculum updates, active conversations occurring on "
"GitHub or other Trainer channels, guest presentations, etc. Upcoming "
"meetings are listed on our Etherpad and on the Community Calendar. If you "
"are not a Trainer, but are interested in joining a meeting, please contact "
"Erin Becker (ebecker@carpentries.org). Minutes for these meetings are "
"available."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_guide.md:6
msgid "Signing up to Teach an Instructor Training Event"
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_guide.md:8
msgid ""
"The Program Manager will send an email to the Trainers list asking all "
"Trainers to fill in their calendar for the upcoming time period. Trainers "
"should sign up for as many days as they are available and hold those dates "
"in their calendar until the schedule is confirmed."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_guide.md:9
msgid ""
"The Program Manager will confirm events with individual Trainers, at which "
"point they are free to release all other dates on their calendar."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_guide.md:10
msgid ""
"The Program Manager will invite member sites to register for upcoming "
"events. Accepted trainees from the open application process will be invited "
"to register one month before each event."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_guide.md:12
msgid ""
"Note that in order to provide the best experience for our trainees, in rare "
"instances events may be canceled due to low enrollment.  If this happens, "
"trainees and Trainers will be notified two weeks before the event.  Trainees"
" will have the opportunity to sign up for a future event."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/trainers_guide.md:14
msgid "A calendar for upcoming instructor training events is here."
msgstr ""

